{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-49","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 49","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Napravi još jedno radio dugme ispod prvog. Smesti ga unutar elementa <code>label</code> sa tekstom <code>Outdoor</code>. Radio dugmetu dodeli atribut <code>id</code> sa vrednošću <code>outdoor</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5f05a1d8e233dff4a68508d8","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-49"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\"> Indoor</label>\n          \n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[36,39],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Samo originalno radio dugme <code>Indoor</code> treba da ima <code>id</code> postavljen na <code>indoor</code>. Ako je potrebno, možeš da resetuješ korak kako bi vratio originalni HTML.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('#indoor').length < 2);"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da praviš nikakve izmene na radio dugmetu <code>Indoor</code>. Ako je potrebno, možeš da resetuješ korak kako bi vratio originalni HTML.</p>","testString":"const indoorInput = document.querySelectorAll('#indoor');\nassert(\n  indoorInput.length == 1 &&\n  indoorInput[0]?.nodeName?.toUpperCase() === 'INPUT' &&\n  indoorInput[0]?.type === 'radio' &&\n  code.match(/<label\\s*>\\s*<input [^>]*(id=[\"']?indoor[\"']?)[^>]*>\\s*Indoor\\s*<\\/label>/)\n);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi dodati novu komponentu za <code>input</code> koja je postavljena unutar nove komponente za <code>label</code>. Proverite da novi <code>label</code> ima otvarajući i zatvarajući tag.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('label input').length === 2);"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da dodaješ nikakve atribute početnoj oznaci elementa <code>label</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/<label\\s*>/g).length === 2);"},{"text":"<p>Novi element <code>input</code> treba da ima atribut <code>id</code> sa vrednošću <code>outdoor</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelector('label input[id=\"outdoor\"]'));"},{"text":"<p>Novi element <code>input</code> treba da ima atribut <code>type</code> sa vrednošću <code>radio</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelector('label input[id=\"outdoor\"][type=\"radio\"]'));"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da dodaješ nove elemente osim elementa <code>input</code> unutar elementa <code>label</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelector('label input[id=\"outdoor\"]:only-child'));"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da bude nikakvog teksta levo od novog elementa <code>input</code>.</p>","testString":"const outdoorBtn = document.querySelector('label input[id=\"outdoor\"]');\nassert(\n    outdoorBtn?.previousSibling?.nodeName !== '#text' ||\n    outdoorBtn?.previousSibling?.nodeValue?.replace(/\\s/g, '') === ''\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tekst etikete za vaš novi radio dugme mora biti tačno <code>Outdoor</code>. Ovo uključuje velika i mala slova.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelector('label > input[id=\"outdoor\"]')?.nextSibling?.nodeValue?.replace(/^\\s+|\\s+$/g, '') === 'Outdoor');"},{"text":"<p>Vaše novo radio dugme i oznaka bi trebalo da budu odmah ispod/nakon radio dugmeta <code>Indoor</code> i njegove oznake. Ne sme biti nijedna druga oznaka između njih.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/<\\/label>\\s*<label\\s*>\\s*<input [^>]+>\\s*Outdoor/i));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-49","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-50","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-48","id":"5f05a1d8e233dff4a68508d8","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-49"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}